        <simpleChoice fixed="false" showHide="show" identifier="B1">車右預知越甲將至，以死勸告齊王務必提前戒備</simpleChoice>
        <simpleChoice fixed="false" showHide="show" identifier="C1">認為齊人忠君愛國，若執意攻伐將招致亡國之禍</simpleChoice>
        <simpleChoice fixed="false" showHide="show" identifier="D1">敬佩雍門子狄敢為死士，畏懼其不惜犧牲的氣勢</simpleChoice>
      </choiceInteraction>
